Quickstrike's crimson optics brightened at the sight of Black 
Arachnia and the sound of a mission. "Alien, huh?" he said, musing 
after his new mission. "But do Solo an' Venomous have t' tage along? 
Solo's got uh few nuts behind th' gears and Venomous don't listen."
